state.unicode: Click to show list of available targets

uientry.s:
local this = UIComponent( Address )
function NotifyParentButtonClicked()
local parent = UIComponent( this:Parent() )
local target_name = UIComponent( this:Find("dy_target") ):GetStateText()
if parent:Id() == "row_entry_window" then
UIComponent( parent:Parent() ):InterfaceFunction( "RowEntryClicked", false, target_name )
elseif parent:Id() == "list_box" then
local multi_parent = UIComponent( UIComponent( parent:Parent() ):Parent() ):Parent() UIComponent( multi_parent ):InterfaceFunction( "RowEntryClicked", true, target_name )
end
end
